Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:35.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I didn't know why we'd received our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:41.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Why we all had come into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:47.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I didn't know how to face the one beside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:51.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Only I looked away and wandered where to love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Though it was always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}If I have a tough, iron armor protecting the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I wonder if I can see you, and beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}I just want to be stronger than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}To hold you, all of, oh even the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:15.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}All the dreams end up as mere dreams, even if game's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}I won't give up my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Even a hope may be said 'Just that's a thought'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}So I still want to reach for you hoping you live your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Only there's a truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:29.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Living for making all the moments shine with proving all times
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Just seeing your smiles, that's my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}Even if we're all even in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:41.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我们是为何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:47.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}爱一直就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:51.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我却总是视若不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}如有足以保护世界的强大钢铁铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}是否能一直见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}迸发无人能及的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,500)}去保护你的心灵 你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:15.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}如果梦想只能作为梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}即使穷途末路 我也不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}抓住零光片羽的希望光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}让你一直能做真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:29.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}我们现在和过去的一切在此绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}你的笑靥 我的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1\fad(200,200)}即使在暗无天日的世界里
