Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:47.52,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\be3\3c&H000000&\3a&H78&}佛罗里达州北部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,被相良打的毫无还手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做不到这种程度 就没法和汞合金战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你基本恢复了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么告诉你个新情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是克拉马提到的地名之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,终于锁定了它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,墨西哥南部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里的沿岸 有地图上没有的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么判断这是汞合金的关联设施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,金钱流向 物流业者 各种方面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,做法和Namsac市很类似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,戒备森严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是小型AS来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,作为对手很难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的部队也吃了很多苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说问题在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个集装箱怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是AS的伪装集装箱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾在内华达的武器展上见过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是地狱君王型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,搭载λ-Driver的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算一个人搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能请你不要扮独狼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底这条情报也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只要用AS奇袭那个什么地狱君主 FXXK到死就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们缺的就是AS啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算没有M9 至少有现行的第二世代机的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那好办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,M6的最新型号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是特种部队用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好说 我可是动员了所有人脉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,人脉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是美国海军的罗伊・希尔兹上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是我原女长官的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,忠实粉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰・柯特尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我听你的在资料上做了手脚把它带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的泰莎亲在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎亲 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}NO！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:42.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\be3\3c&H000000&\3a&H78&}墨西哥近海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人的增援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有确定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但在近海探测到了可疑的声源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,巨兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要中止作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可是要进行侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我叫克鲁佐先生来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:20.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\be3\3c&H000000&\3a&H78&}墨西哥·米却肯州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Ag
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在听吗 Mr.Ag
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你手上的那个小姑娘 千鸟要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,秘银残党似乎发现了你们的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩对于卡利俄佩计划不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不应该转移吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的她需要一个放松的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们也派出增援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,巨兽和地狱君王 各三台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是大军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么拒绝的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 请便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,雷纳德大人 Mr.K到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让你久等了吧 Mr.K
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次任务感想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要看俘获的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他们的王牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,失望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,核心单元已经拆出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是准备周到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,处理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,会议如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在预料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会派增援过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以增援为名 袭击这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是我这样诱导的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 可能已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为了呼应上层的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,美军特种部队似乎有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说汞合金掌握了美军的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要过于期待比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让我等好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 卡斯帕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.K 又名…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 在这一行可是名人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到会在这里遇到世界屈指一数的狙击手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就全体到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,开始欢迎委员会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.27,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\be3\3c&H000000&\3a&H78&}尼克罗近郊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,倒数一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是代号Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 Uruz7 祝好运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你收拾一下行李
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚恐怕就要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对笼中鸟什么都不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早晚会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人？ 不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,M9
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,M9 是秘银的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是我没见过的机种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是美军的M9吧 多半是陆军的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,终于投入实战了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,至少目标不是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,美军的AS被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,奇袭已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,作战中止 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人被美军吸引了注意 正是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太乱来了 回来 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还来得及 我会赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}千鸟 就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他把通信切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让巴代的别动队撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去他们也会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是让人看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你开着那种机体来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你用的频段相同 所以都让我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全都被偷听光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对面一口一句宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是克鲁兹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你还活着啊 阴郁男
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有很多想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但似乎对面来援兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我发情报给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,地狱君王型两台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,奇袭想必已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们见识专家的厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小子们 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,随时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,随地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock'n Roll
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边 忍者混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先干掉一台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,克鲁兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去的不是那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心思都写在脸上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但你非去不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz2 击破两台地狱君王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正和剩余的一台交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 在遇敌之际确认了相良宗介的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相良吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,活蹦乱跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看来和我们的目标一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要似乎在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 你也多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 通信结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,相良 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,贝恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ephemere1 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我和秘银的战友汇合 击破了两台地狱君主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,战友 能信得过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也有消息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才和某人接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是自称幽灵的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她准备了备用的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要是情况不妙 就去坐标41A待机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,美军那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来士气低落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,8点钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和刚才的敌人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,久候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 欢迎你们 秘银的各位残党
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是福勒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们的奋斗致以敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也差不多该做个了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,包围网已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,扔掉武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起了赫尔马基斯坦呢 相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,少校 这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我成了汞合金的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢抵抗 我就下令射杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 千鸟就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要知道 扔下武器投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,照他说的去做比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雷纳德・泰斯塔罗莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,千鸟 千鸟 千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是没什么长进呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Au的部队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,露出本性了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 要拿他怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,“试着阻止我吧”？
Comment: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================C-PART=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,反正只有那个男人才能用它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介万一死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,扔掉或者破坏掉随你处置
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 Make my day
